WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:03.800
<i>Hi, I'm Chuck. Here's a few
things you might need to know.</i>

00:04.200 --> 00:06.000
<i>SARAH:
You're not the same guy
that I fell for.</i>

00:06.000 --> 00:07.000
How am I not the same guy?

00:07.000 --> 00:08.100
You killed somebody, Chuck.

00:08.100 --> 00:09.900
He didn't kill the mole.
What?

00:11.200 --> 00:13.400
<i>I did.
It's time you learned the truth</i>

00:13.400 --> 00:14.800
about your
wife's murder.

00:16.600 --> 00:17.700
No!

00:17.700 --> 00:20.100
If the Ring
<i>played him this video...</i>

00:20.200 --> 00:21.900
Oh, my God, General,
where is Sarah now?

00:22.000 --> 00:23.600
I believe she's with Agent Shaw.

00:23.600 --> 00:25.100
Daniel, where are
you taking us?

00:27.300 --> 00:28.500
To settle an old score.

