00:48.000 --> 00:50.800
Okay, just give me 20 seconds.
Are you sure about this?

00:50.800 --> 00:52.500
NSA picked up
the Director's signal.

00:52.700 --> 00:54.100
This is his
broadcast point.

00:55.000 --> 00:55.900
If they're right, Sarah,

00:56.000 --> 00:58.000
the Ring's most senior operative
is behind that door.

01:04.000 --> 01:04.800
Cover me.

01:09.000 --> 01:10.600
Hey, buddy.
Hey.

01:10.600 --> 01:12.000
Hey, hey, buddy.
Where's Casey?

01:12.000 --> 01:13.000
Haven't seen him.
I have been thinking

01:13.000 --> 01:14.700
about this whole unofficial
member of Operation Bartowski

01:14.700 --> 01:16.000
and I'd like
to make it official.

01:16.000 --> 01:18.100
Yeah, you know, I'm kind of
in the middle of something...
Spyish?

01:18.100 --> 01:19.600
I know. That's my point,
dude. Let me help.

01:19.600 --> 01:21.000
I want to be
part of the team.
Okay, fine.

01:21.000 --> 01:22.500
Help me find Casey
and you're part of the team.

01:22.600 --> 01:24.200
Operation Bartowski?
I could actually...

01:25.000 --> 01:26.700
Not so loud.
Not so loud, right.

01:26.700 --> 01:27.600
It's just great
news, you know,

01:27.600 --> 01:30.000
because, listen, I could be
your second in command
slash personal assistant.

01:30.200 --> 01:31.200
Batman needs Alfred.

01:31.200 --> 01:31.800
Bond needs Q.

01:31.800 --> 01:34.300
Chuck-- hey, hey, hey.
You need me.

01:34.300 --> 01:35.600
Morgan, I need Casey right now.

01:35.600 --> 01:37.800
Well, Chuck, per my excellent
peripheral vision--

01:38.000 --> 01:39.600
which is a valuable spy skill
I might add--

01:39.600 --> 01:42.600
I can tell you that
one John Casey is
now exiting the restroom.

01:44.300 --> 01:45.900
Oh, thank you. Great.
You're welcome.

01:47.000 --> 01:48.200
So I'm a spy?
That's it? Official?

01:48.200 --> 01:49.400
Yes, you're a spy. Gotta go.

01:50.000 --> 01:50.900
I am a spy.

02:01.400 --> 02:02.400
Shaw?

02:03.600 --> 02:05.500
Walker killed Shaw's wife?

02:05.500 --> 02:07.800
It was five years ago.
It was her Red Test.

02:07.800 --> 02:10.600
Sarah didn't know.
Beckman didn't know, but Shaw,
he knows.

02:10.600 --> 02:13.000
Now, he and Sarah have
disappeared on some mission.
They're off the grid.

02:13.000 --> 02:14.800
They can't be raised.
They're gone.
Chuck, I'm not an agent.

02:14.800 --> 02:16.100
You shouldn't be
telling me any of this.

02:16.100 --> 02:17.700
But you know what to do, Casey.

02:18.000 --> 02:19.400
Okay, Beckman told me
to just sit tight.

02:19.400 --> 02:20.600
You and I know
I can't do that.

02:23.600 --> 02:24.800
Sarah just activated
her locator.

02:24.800 --> 02:25.800
She's in trouble.

02:27.400 --> 02:28.200
Come on, man!

02:28.200 --> 02:29.600
You know how I feel about her.

02:32.500 --> 02:33.500
Call this number.

02:33.500 --> 02:34.700
Request Tactical Support.

02:34.700 --> 02:36.700
You'll be forwarded
to a Colonel Sanders.

02:37.400 --> 02:38.400
Don't make fun of his name.

02:38.600 --> 02:40.700
You want air,
armor-- everything.

03:03.100 --> 03:05.300
...video camera
for your birthday.

03:05.400 --> 03:08.300
I had no idea you were
going to use my present
against me.

03:09.800 --> 03:11.000
Happy birthday.

03:12.400 --> 03:13.800
I love you.

03:15.700 --> 03:16.700
Oh, my God.

03:22.400 --> 03:23.800
I love you.

03:43.100 --> 03:45.000
All right, one more time,
just so we're clear.

03:45.000 --> 03:46.600
We have to reacquire
Agent Walker.

03:46.600 --> 03:49.000
Nothing can happen to her.
Do I make myself clear?

03:49.000 --> 03:50.100
Yes, sir.
Yes, sir.
Yes, sir.

03:51.000 --> 03:52.700
This is Team Leader.
Is everything set?

03:53.000 --> 03:53.800
Air is go.

03:54.000 --> 03:54.900
Mechanized is go.

03:55.200 --> 03:56.000
Tactical is go.

03:56.100 --> 03:57.200
Airborne is go.

03:58.000 --> 03:59.200
All right, boys,
let's do this.

04:17.200 --> 04:18.300
Shaw.

04:26.000 --> 04:26.900
I'm going first.

04:30.500 --> 04:31.400
Shaw.

04:32.000 --> 04:33.400
What is going on?

04:38.800 --> 04:41.100
What is this?
This is my Red Test.

04:41.100 --> 04:43.900
Why would they have
my surveillance footage
from my first kill?

04:44.800 --> 04:45.900
Just take a breath.

04:47.700 --> 04:50.000
This is the worst
moment of my life
up there on that monitor.

04:51.400 --> 04:53.000
I love you.

04:54.800 --> 04:55.900
Mine, too.

04:56.000 --> 04:56.900
What?

04:57.800 --> 04:58.800
Why? Who is she?

05:01.000 --> 05:02.000
Evelyn Shaw.

05:04.700 --> 05:06.600
I killed your wife?

05:07.200 --> 05:09.400
?

05:12.400 --> 05:14.100
You had no idea that
the Ring was behind this.

05:14.100 --> 05:15.600
Shaw, I killed your wife.

05:15.600 --> 05:17.600
This isn't your fault.
I thought I was a good spy.

05:17.700 --> 05:19.400
This isn't your fault.

05:24.000 --> 05:24.900
Hey... it's okay.

05:38.800 --> 05:39.600
Chuck?

05:44.600 --> 05:47.700
Go! Go! Go! Go! Go!

05:47.700 --> 05:48.800
Move! Move! Move!

05:48.800 --> 05:49.800
The perimeter's surrounded.
Put your hands up!

05:49.800 --> 05:51.200
Down on the ground now!

05:51.900 --> 05:53.000
Now! Now!

05:53.000 --> 05:54.200
?

05:54.200 --> 05:55.000
MAN (over radio):
What's happening in there?

05:55.300 --> 05:56.200
Target's secure?

05:57.800 --> 05:58.700
This is Team Leader.

05:59.200 --> 06:00.200
Cancel air support.

06:00.200 --> 06:01.200
Cancel tactical.

06:04.800 --> 06:05.800
And the tank, the tank!

06:05.800 --> 06:06.600
Cancel the tank.

